{
  "stem": "23131.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He asked the commander that was with them if I can take it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, go ahead and take it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in the jacket, in the back of his jacket, in the inside pocket, he found a letter-- a German letter-- which was placed in Ro-- in Minsk when they started, you know, after the war.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The SA document said-- big letter from the Germans-- thank you so much for helping us out to-- to kill the Jews, to find them, and for sending your son to-- to the place-- to the right place.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you'll be awarded for it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They award anybody 400,000 ruble for-- to catch my husband, to-- to catch him or to kill him or to bring him alive.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Germans.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It started slowly-- 300, 400, 750.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then we had to go to a very big-- the Germans made a big-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Raid on us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were ten days in-- in water.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And everybody survived-- small kids.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was already in [INAUDIBLE] This was already in the deep woods of the labor camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In dumps and water.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No food, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And every-- not one person was missing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the-- when the group was already so big, it was established-- my husband had a choice-- I told you.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To stay with the older and young, and children, or to leave them and-- and go on his own.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He never accepted it, no matter how.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And believe me, there was plenty problems.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As if-- as today, there's different problems in life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was problems because our Jews cannot sit still.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Like I mentioned, they wanted-- everybody wanted to be in the command.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Commander can be the only one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they find different things.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
